flowchart TD
    Start([SQS Message Received]) --> LoadState[Load state from DynamoDB]
    LoadState --> Route{Dispatcher Route}

    Route -->|sender=broker| Ignore[Log broker_ignored<br/>No tools called]
    Route -->|event=tracking| Tracking{Distance ≤ geofence?}
    Route -->|event=communication<br/>sender≠broker| Agent[Agent Tool Loop]

    Tracking -->|No| ResetStreak[Reset ping streak]
    Tracking -->|Yes| IncrStreak[Increment streak]
    IncrStreak --> Check3{Streak ≥ 3?}
    Check3 -->|No| Done1[Keep state<br/>on_route_to_delivery]
    Check3 -->|Yes| Arrival[update_load_state → at_delivery<br/>cancel_timers]

    Agent --> LLM[Call LLM with tools schema]
    LLM --> ToolCalls{Tool calls returned?}
    ToolCalls -->|Yes| Execute[Execute tools<br/>Record results]
    Execute --> FeedBack[Feed results back to LLM]
    FeedBack --> LLM
    ToolCalls -->|No / finish_reason=stop| ParseDecision[Parse decision]

    ParseDecision --> UpdateState[Update load state if changed]

    Ignore --> Persist
    Done1 --> Persist
    Arrival --> Persist
    ResetStreak --> Persist
    UpdateState --> Persist

    Persist[Persist to DynamoDB<br/>version++ conditional update] --> WriteEvents[Write event record]
    WriteEvents --> WriteTools[Write tool_call records]
    WriteTools --> JSONL[Write JSONL trace]
    JSONL --> End([Done])

    style Start fill:#e1f5fe
    style End fill:#e1f5fe
    style Ignore fill:#9e9e9e,color:#fff
    style Arrival fill:#4caf50,color:#fff
    style Agent fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
    style LLM fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style Execute fill:#2196f3,color:#fff
    style Persist fill:#1565c0,color:#fff
